hot environments during competition.

139
00:08:28,460 --> 00:08:31,210
Endurance athletes may have irregular
menstrual cycles,

140
00:08:31,210 --> 00:08:34,239
which makes it harder for them to know
whether they are pregnant.

141
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:38,570
If you think you might be pregnant, or
trying to get pregnant,

142
00:08:38,570 --> 00:08:42,910
be careful of hot tubs, or hot baths
lasting more than then minutes, and

143
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:47,040
prolonged, intense exercise that raises
body temperature.

144
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,490
Also if you have a fever,

145
00:08:48,490 --> 00:08:52,850
be sure to seek medical assistance to
manage your symptoms in a safe way.

146
00:08:52,850 --> 00:08:55,840
If you think you've been hyperthermic
during your pregnancy, you should talk

147
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:59,460
